<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--left stage6-tool-side">
    <div class="stage6-side-title">
        <span class="stage6-step-badge">STEP 06</span>
        <strong>최종 꾸미기</strong>
        <small>왼쪽은 도구만, 세부 편집은 오른쪽 선택 요소에서 처리합니다.</small>
    </div>

    <section class="stage6-panel stage6-panel--tools">
        <h3>도구</h3>
        <div class="stage6-tool-grid" id="stage6ToolGrid">
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool is-active" data-tool="move" title="선택 / 이동 / 구역 라벨 이동">
                <span>↕</span><b>이동</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool" data-tool="text" title="텍스트 추가">
                <span>T</span><b>텍스트</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool" data-tool="rect" title="사각형 추가">
                <span>▭</span><b>박스</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool" data-tool="ellipse" title="원형 추가">
                <span>◯</span><b>원형</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool" data-tool="line" title="선 추가">
                <span>╱</span><b>선</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-tool" data-tool="erase" title="선택 요소 삭제">
                <span>⌫</span><b>지우개</b>
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage6-panel stage6-panel--compact">
        <h3>자동</h3>
        <button type="button" class="stage6-quick stage6-quick--single" id="importSectionLabels">구역 라벨 생성</button>
    </section>

    <section class="stage6-panel stage6-panel--compact">
        <h3>보기</h3>
        <div class="stage6-view-strip">
            <label class="stage6-view-chip"><input type="checkbox" id="toggleSections" checked><span>구역</span></label>
            <label class="stage6-view-chip"><input type="checkbox" id="toggleLabels" checked><span>라벨</span></label>
            <label class="stage6-view-chip"><input type="checkbox" id="toggleSeats"><span>좌석</span></label>
            <label class="stage6-view-chip"><input type="checkbox" id="toggleBooking"><span>버튼</span></label>
            <label class="stage6-view-chip"><input type="checkbox" id="toggleCompare"><span>원본</span></label>
        </div>
    </section>
</aside>

<main class="seatmap-main stage6-canvas-main">
    <div class="stage6-canvas-head">
        <div>
            <strong>최종 도면 캔버스</strong>
            <span id="stage6CanvasInfo">도면을 불러오는 중...</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage6-canvas-head__tools">
            <button type="button" id="resetCanvasView">100%</button>
            <button type="button" id="fitCanvasViewInline">화면 맞춤</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stage6-canvas-viewport" id="stage6CanvasViewport">
        <div class="stage6-canvas-board" id="stage6CanvasBoard">
            <canvas id="canvas"></canvas>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage6-right-side">
    <section class="stage6-panel">
        <h3>선택 요소</h3>
        <div class="stage6-selected-box" id="selectedObjectInfo">
            아직 선택된 요소가 없습니다.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage6-panel">
        <div class="stage6-panel-head">
            <h3>레이어</h3>
            <button type="button" class="stage6-inline-btn" id="clearSelection">선택 해제</button>
        </div>
        <div class="stage6-layer-list" id="layerList">
            <div class="stage6-empty-layer">추가된 꾸미기 요소가 없습니다.</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage6-panel">
        <h3>미니맵</h3>
        <div class="stage6-minimap-wrap">
            <canvas id="stage6MiniMap" width="260" height="170"></canvas>
        </div>
        <p class="stage6-help">구역은 이동 도구 상태에서 바로 클릭하면 선택됩니다. 상단 저장/작업취소/다시실행/확대·축소 버튼과 연동됩니다.</p>
    </section>
</aside>
